data.description: Welcome home! This great home features three bedroom two full bathroom home is right by the Dewey O Boster Sports Complex, Walmart, shopping and dining at Saxon Crossing, Lake Monroe and Lyonia Preserve, with quick access to I4. Enjoy the weekends fishing, hiking, and relaxing at the nearby parks, take a visit to the Central Florida Zoo, or stroll around historic downtown Sanford, sprawling with breweries and boutiques. This freshly remodeled beauty sits on a spacious lot with a long driveway, two car garage and spacious fenced in yard. Inside you’ll be greeted by wood laminate floors, a neutral color palette, and all new finishes. The formal living and dining wrap around to the kitchen, family room and bonus space with vaulted ceilings, which would be perfect for a home office. The kitchen presents beautiful cabinets, two pantries, a tray ceiling, stainless steel appliances and an abundance of storage space. The family room offers soaring ceilings and French doors with blinds between the glass, leading to the outdoor patio. The master suite features an open bathroom with an updated vanity, a luxurious private shower with beautiful tile, and a walk in closet. The master suite also has sliding doors to a privately fenced in side yard. This space would make for a wonderful garden or meditation and zen space. The other two bedrooms are located on the other side of the home, adjacent to the updated guest bath with a tub/shower combo. BRAND NEW ROOF JUNE OF 2023.
